{"word":"ἕσις","slug":"ἕσις","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἕσις</b></el> <el>(ἕσις, εως) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἵημι'><el>ἵημι</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>an impulse, tendency</i>, only in <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>: but the <a href='S:compound'>compd.</a> <el>ἔφεσις</el> is found.<p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>(<el>ἕζω</el>) <i>a sitting.</i> <a href='S:vide'>v.</a> <el>εἰς-.</el><p/></div>"}]}